{
  "stem": "27507.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, that must have happened later that-- than I maybe gave the impression before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it happened only in the late 1941, probably in autumn or thereabout of 1941.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had no place to move to to start.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we lived-- for a while I think we lived with our family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We lived with-- in [POLISH] Street, which I mentioned before, where most of the family of my mother lived.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was a flat, I think, on the ground floor, if remember correctly, not terribly big.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was all similar, to mind, it slightly goes together with the flat where the Szenfelds, the family of my mother, lived where my-- my grandparents, my maternal grandparents fled in [POLISH] Street, where they lived before the war.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was another not terribly big flat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was always full of people, because there were so many of members of the family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was my aunt Hania, who was teaching English in one room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were three or four other members of the family, my uncle Yeziek and my uncle Sevek and [INAUDIBLE] and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were in the front room discussing something and that was as well the place where they were eating, because there was a big table there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was somehow very often there in those days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was even sleeping there, although there were so many people, I'm not quite sure anymore how I managed to sleep.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I think one got used to everything, and I was even able to sleep with the light and with people being there all around me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there were as well my younger cousins.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
